Pre-Game Insights: The Proteas' fixtures for the Super 8 stage of the 2024 T20 World Cup have been confirmed.
The undefeated Proteas earned a place in Group 2, along with defending champions England, as well as co-hosts West Indies and the USA.
The first match of the Super 8's sees South Africa face tournament surprise package USA at Sir Vivian Richards Stadium in Antigua on Wednesday 19 June.
The US outfit defeated Canada in the tournament opener and then Pakistan via a Super Over, helping them sneak into the Super 8's.
